{"tid":2207991,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)超人歐布前傳","createTime":"2020-09-18T14:05:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T18:09:21.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f9b14352e43b049b266371805158d4aceb56274b","tid":2207991,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T14:05:26.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">新沙士已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdezNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=764f7e70\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdezNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=e07033e9\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdezNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=8d4b2874\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wfGY537.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwfGY537.jpg&h=256cfa0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《歐布奧特曼：原生之初》是《歐布奧特曼》的前傳作品，講述歐布奧特曼即紅凱與伽古拉斯&middot;伽古拉初次獲得力量的故事。<br />\n講述的是從歷代奧特戰士那獲取力量的浪客凱和伽古拉斯&middot;伽古拉的故事。凱和伽古拉生活在同一顆星球，他們曾是並肩作戰的好夥伴，在歷經磨難登上勇士之巔後，凱意外被選為歐布奧特曼。他們的首次任務就是拯救王立行星伽農。在王立行星伽農上有一棵參天大樹&ldquo;生命之樹&rdquo;，這顆行星的女王不希望星球上發生戰爭，如果&ldquo;生命之樹&rdquo;被採伐的話，星球上的人就會失去保護，而女王最終決定化身為戰神。凱為了拯救王立行星伽農，一路上遇到了許許多多的人和奧特戰士，在此過程中他漸漸有了成為奧特戰士的覺悟<br />\n<br />\n10 20PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdezNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=939e337c\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdezNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=25a749c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c77b10bf4864791b64bda12645e44db1584585","tid":2207991,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T14:08:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ff6bf3376497778a91760980a1bc14b721e732f","tid":2207991,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T15:03:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ca9c0a3d0a17af4d85208ec7fe2e0b99799079e","tid":2207991,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T16:18:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=